title: Harmony Fire Department to hold pasta dinner fundraiser May 21
content: The Harmony Fire Department & Improvement Association will hold their 2nd annual pasta dinner fundraiser on Tuesday, May 21 at 194 Putnam Pike from 5 to 9 p.m. Dinner costs $10 per person and children under age 10 are free. Tickets can be purchased from any member.
author: ByEditorial team-
